headline: Realtor.com速 Monthly Housing Report: Inventory Keeps Growing, but 2025 Revealed a Market of Exceptions, Not Averages
summary: U.S. housing inventory continued to expand in December, marking the 26th consecutive month of year-over-year gains, but the Realtor.com速 December Monthly Housing Report shows that 2025 was defined less by broad national trends and more by stark local differences that often ran counter to regional narratives.
